### Get all tickets (no filter)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets

### Filter tickets by status = OPEN
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?status=OPEN

### Filter tickets by priority = HIGH
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?priority=HIGH

### Filter tickets by category = Email
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets?category=Email

### Get one ticket by ID (replace with real ID from GET /api/tickets)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/REPLACE_WITH_REAL_ID

### Get a missing ticket (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/000000000000000000000000

### Create a new ticket
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cannot connect to VPN",
  "description": "VPN connection fails with timeout error",
  "category": "Network",
  "priority": "HIGH",
  "createdBy": "alice@example.com"
}

### Create an invalid ticket (missing required fields)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "",
  "category": "",
  "priority": "",
  "createdBy": ""
}
